              wa-ʿajāʾib al-asfār</title>
            <author>Ibn Baṭṭūta</author>
            <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/bibl/QVIUC5ZC"/>
            <citedRange unit="pp">146, 153, 154</citedRange>
